Package: erlang-fs-listener
Version: 4.1-2
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Ejabberd Packaging Team <ejabberd@packages.debian.org>
Installed-Size: 65
Depends: erlang-base (>= 1:19.2) | erlang-abi-17.0, erlang-base (>= 1:20.3.6+dfsg) | erlang-base-hipe (>= 1:20.3.6+dfsg), inotify-tools
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Homepage: http://synrc.github.io/fs/
Description: Erlang filesystem listener
 This library implements a filesystem listener for Erlang via inotify-tools.
 It allows one to subscribe to notifications and list events from the backend.
 An API allows for versatile use cases.
